Description:
You arrive at the entrance of a cave full of cobwebs, it is obvious that it is from this cave that all the spiders that you have been killing come from.

This is undoubtedly the cave that the figure in the shadows of Senenthia's watermill spoke of. You enter the cave to search for the strong venom.

As you enter, the ground below you begins to collapse.
DescriptionAction: You have to try something to avoid falling.
